Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい　起きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北東戦域で拾った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前はつけてない　「お前」で呼んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい　挨拶しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乱暴はよせ　こんな子供に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:27.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギル　そいつは子供じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そいつは武器だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:35.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただの戦う道具だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった　この子は引き取る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうか　受け取ってくれてよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:47.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陸軍にはもう　話はつけてある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディートフリート・ブーゲンビリア大佐にお会いしたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから　大佐は面会できないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}急ぎ確認したいことがあるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しつこいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:35.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐　申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの女が　しつこく大佐を出せと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前は下がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死にたくなかったらな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここで何をしている？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やはり　武器は武器だな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐が　ギルベルト少佐が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:08.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未帰還だというのは事実でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知らなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルトは　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウソです　ウソです 少佐はご無事です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ　その顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつにとってただの道具だった貴様が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情のないただの道具の貴様が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悲しいはずはないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしてしゃべっちゃったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　今の彼女なら受け止められるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:41.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた　いっつも見極めが甘すぎるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相変わらず女心が分かってないし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とにかく　さっさとあの子を捜しに行きなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら　坊ちゃま
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その子は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とりあえず　風呂に入れて　服を着替えさせてやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの…　奥様には
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様は今　ライデンのお屋敷に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知らせる必要はない しばらくの間　私が預かることになった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっちにいらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛い　ちょっとやめて　イタタ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坊ちゃま　着替えさせたのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この子が暴れるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　いいんだ　かまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:04.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}食事をさせたら　客間に連れて行ってくれ　頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風邪を…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:19.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風邪を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛布を使うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明日も寒くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待ちなさい　ダメよ　外に出ては
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:45.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この子　ずっと坊ちゃまを捜していて　食事もとらずに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前線には連れて行きません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの少女は不安定すぎます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぜ反対する？　上層部からの命令だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}演習場でのヤツの姿を君も見ただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:09.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人をあやめるだけが取り柄で　他に何の役にも立たん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連れて行ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうムキになるな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身寄りのない娘一人　使えるだけ使って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}役に立たなくなれば　戦場に捨ててくればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子は　まだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}くだらん　まったく　君の偽善には付き合っておれん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令だ　以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ガルダリク連合軍はボチアッチャに侵攻を開始した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただちに　ボチアッチャの首都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カプリア前面の川で防衛線を張ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在は持久戦に突入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こちらの軍勢は三万　相手は六万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}持ちこたえているが　敵は前線に大砲を送ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それ以降　その砲撃によって士気は低下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦線崩壊の可能性もある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこで　ブーゲンビリア少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君に中隊を率いて　砲の破壊に当たってもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ　必ず成功させてみせます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は　ここにいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が戻るまで動くんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐　準備整いました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すぐ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐　見張りの兵です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ　何があった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敵襲　敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本隊へ連絡　ライデンシャフトリヒの襲撃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}応戦しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長　敵が近くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:32.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐は　少佐はいらっしゃいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐は　こちらに　いらっしゃるのですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坊ちゃまは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:04.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ギルベルト・ブーゲンビリア」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の…　お名前が…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　ヴァイオレットだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:18.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は道具ではなく　その名が似合う人になるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言葉は分かるんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しょうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレ…　レット
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:40.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだ　君がヴァイオレットで　私が少佐だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しょうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しょうさ　読みました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よし　今度は書くことも覚えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐　報告書です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よく書けている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}字の練習にもなるから　これから毎日報告書を出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かったね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毎日　報告書を出します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8}坊ちゃまは…　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:23.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつは確認できなかったが　ガレキの下に認識票があった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8}亡くなったギルベルトも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで　未帰還扱いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルトは　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝祭だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:43.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年の間　ここはガルダリク軍に占拠されていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:44.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっと解放された
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　君の功績だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この町　メヒティッヒの感謝祭は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝を捧げる人に　贈り物をするのが習わしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何か欲しい物はあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欲しい物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだ　何でも欲しい物を言いなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　少佐が命令されるのでしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:21.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が君に感謝したいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだ　いつも　よく戦って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少し歩こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:37.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:43.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は何を欲しがるのが適切なのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君くらいの女の子なら　ドレスやアクセサリー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ドレスやアクセサリーを欲しがります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の瞳があります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の瞳と同じ色です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これを見た時の
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こういうのを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何と言うのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうです　美しいブローチでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うつくしい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「うつくしい」は知りませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「きれい」と似ている言葉ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の瞳と同じ色でなくてよかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:13.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ　これが一番「美しい」でした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言葉が分からなかったので　言ったことはありませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出会った時から「美しい」です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:38.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ブローチを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ガルダリクの連中　西の基地からも撤退したってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}春までにはうちに帰れるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}みんなで帰ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルト
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久しぶりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズ中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中佐はよせ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうはいかない　階級は君のほうが上だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前のそのそっけない態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久しぶりだと可愛く見えるから不思議だな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君も変わらないな　中佐になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:57.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺の場合は戦わずして勝つような戦線ばかりに投入されてきたし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の家は戦費の大出資元なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}軍本部が配慮するのはしかたない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから出世するのも肩身が狭いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それより　お前　元気にしてたか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飯　食べてるか　ちゃんと寝てんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これは　ふぜけただけだ　楽にしていい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私より年は上だが　彼は士官学校の同期だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前に訓練所で見た…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ手元に置いていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この子だろ　カプリアの戦いで　すさまじい戦功を挙げたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の「武器」だって　ひそかにウワサになってるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他に　させることがあるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　すまない　えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前がなかったので　私がつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}インテンス奪還作戦にもその子を？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この作戦が成功すれば　敵は総崩れになる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐らく　それが最後の戦いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:15.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺さ　この戦争が終わったら軍を辞めて　会社を興そうかと思ってるんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会社？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そしたら　お前も雇ってやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の下で働くのは気が進まんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　ヴァイオレットちゃんを雇うことにしろか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はもうご不要ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}処分される結果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズ中佐のもとへ移されるのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:07.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう　少佐に命令は頂けないのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう数時間で決戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この話は　また今度にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作戦を説明する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このインテンスには敵軍の総本部がある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}周りを断崖に囲まれた　まさに自然の要塞だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正面からの突破は難しいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこで　まず主攻部隊が砲撃を仕掛ける
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:45.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その隙に　我々が地下水道からインテンス内部に侵入し
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大聖堂に突入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本部を制圧する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その後　信号弾を上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:55.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味方に全軍突入の合図を送れば　作戦は終了だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}砲撃五分前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よし　行け
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}砲撃開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}砲撃開始　て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}続け
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各班　状況報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一班　三人がやられました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二班は　ほぼ無傷です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:59.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三班四班は半数が脱落　厳しい状況です
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:00.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一班二班は周囲を制圧して　敵の増援を近づけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:09.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三班四班の残りの者は私と共に大聖堂を制圧する
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}て
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルト　うまくやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}て
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右へ回れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:40.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全軍突撃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐！
Comment: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在东北战区捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没取名字 都是用「你」来叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 快打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别对小孩这么粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:27.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔 那家伙不是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:35.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是个战斗的道具罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}知道了 我收留她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗 你愿意收下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:47.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和陆军省那边已经谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要见迪特福利特·布干维尔大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都说了 大佐谢绝会面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我有急事要向他确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:35.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大佐 十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个女的非得要大佐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们退下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不想死就照办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果然 武器就是武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 基尔伯特少佐他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:08.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}阵亡了 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你撒谎 你撒谎 少佐他一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你对他来说只是个道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这没有感情的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么会感到悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你怎么就告诉她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在的她应该能够接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:41.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你总是把事情想得太简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还是这么不懂女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总之 快去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总之先让她洗个澡 换件衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那要怎么向老夫人交代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老夫人现在在莱顿的宅子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不用告诉她 暂时由我来收留她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好痛 喂住手 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少爷 让她换好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可这孩子闹个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:04.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}给她吃完饭就带到客厅来 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}会感冒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:19.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}盖好毛毯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明天还会变冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等 不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:45.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这孩子一直在找少爷 连饭也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不能把她带去前线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那位少女太不稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么反对 这可是上层下达的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她在演习场上的表现你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:09.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}除了杀人一无所长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}带去试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别这么认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:18.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一个无亲无故的女孩子 尽管利用就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没用了就把她在战场上随处一扔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那孩子才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无聊透顶 没空奉陪你的伪善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是命令 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}加达里克联军开始进攻波契阿查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然立刻在波契阿查的首都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}卡普利亚前方河边筑起了防线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但现已拖入持久战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我军人数为三万 敌军为六万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然还能坚持 但敌军在前线投入了大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}遭受炮击后我方士气低落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}防线可能会被攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因此 布干维尔少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你率领中队 前去破坏大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是 保证完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你就待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在我回来之前别动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 有哨兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}敌袭！敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快联络总队 莱顿沙夫特里希的袭击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}准备迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}队长 敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲锋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:32.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…少佐他在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:04.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特·布干维尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 就叫薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:18.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你将不再是道具，而是成为人如其名的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔…莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你听得懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉…莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:40.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错 你是薇尔莉特 我是少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 我读完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 接下来就学写字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐 这是报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}顺便还能练字 今后每天都提交报告书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我每天提交报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\an8}少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:23.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然没能找到他 但在瓦砾下有他的识别牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\an8}逝去的基尔伯特也能瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后就作阵亡处理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天是感恩节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:43.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三年间 这里被加达里克军占领
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:44.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如今终于解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 这是你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这座城市 梅赫德希的感恩节有个习俗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是送东西给想感谢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你有什么想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想要的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:10.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错 有什么想要的就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的 既然少佐命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:21.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我想对你表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 你一直都英勇奋战…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}稍微走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:37.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:43.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想要什么东西 才算合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}像你这个年纪的女孩子 会要裙子 首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想要裙子 首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有少佐的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和少佐的眼睛是一样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看到它的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}该怎么形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么样 这个胸针很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不太懂什么是「美」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是和「漂亮」相似的词语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和你眼睛的颜色不一样 真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:13.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事 这个是最「美」的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:19.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不懂它的意思 所以没有这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是少佐的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从我遇见少佐的时候就觉得它很美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:38.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}胸针给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听说加达里克的西部基地也撤兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}春天之前能回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}霍金斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别叫我中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那可不行 你的军衔比我高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好久没见你这冷淡的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没想到还挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也是老样子啊 哪怕当了中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:57.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去的战线尽是不战而胜的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你家里是赞助军费的大户
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}军队总部自然会照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以就算升职了也很不光彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}话说回来 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好好吃饭没有啊 好好睡觉没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是开玩笑 不用紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然他比我年长 但我们在士官学校是同届
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之前在训练场见过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你还把她留在身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在卡普利亚的战斗中立下赫赫战功的人就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家都在传 说是少佐的「武器」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有别的事能安排她做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她叫薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她之前没有名字 是我给她起的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因坦斯夺回作战也要带上这孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这次作战能成功的话 敌人就会全线崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}恐怕这将是最后的战役
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:15.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等战争结束 我打算退伍去开个公司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到时候也会雇佣你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我可提不起劲在你手下干活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我就雇下薇尔莉特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您已经不需要我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作为处分的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会被转到霍金斯中佐手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:07.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我再也收不到少佐的命令了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}几个小时后就是决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这些话下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说明一下作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:31.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}敌军的总部就在因坦斯这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}四周都是悬崖 可谓是天然的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}正面突破太困难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以 先由主攻部队进行炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:45.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们趁机从下水道入侵因坦斯内部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲进大圣堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}占领敌方总部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之后发射信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:55.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通知全体友军突入 作战到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有五分钟开始炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}炮击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}炮击开始 开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}各班 汇报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一班被干掉三人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}二班几乎没伤
